{"tid":2105942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參展商稱收書展延期通知　關注組：或延至9月或12月","createTime":"2020-07-13T03:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T05:00:25.000Z","uid":60281,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8c3ebe45189691a8ab264aeedd4d7b544d510561","tid":2105942,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n消息指，政府高層正召開會議，商討一系列收緊防疫措施，包括是否舉行書展，預料最快今日公布。消息又指，當局傾向將書展延期。 有參展商指，剛剛已經收到通知，書展將會延期。2020香港書展關注組指，多個參展商中午前都收到通知，又指收到來自貿發局的消息，指書展可能會延期至9月或12月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346784&d=Z5C23SoLFrdwUrTWaDZosxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=fb53bd14\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346784</a>"},{"pid":"9b8487debad7a020bc75ba47f68961bedb61ca54","tid":2105942,"uid":68689,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"貿然延期將會跌入圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db70bd808bc98d7b495adb1c50ea723aff8be582","tid":2105942,"uid":11008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"咁迪士尼同海洋公園呢？d 病毒有基本法保護識轉彎唔會感染？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12afe8dc77c3a9d9cf340c2c8b1b00b2a94ca467","tid":2105942,"uid":60924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db70bd808bc98d7b495adb1c50ea723aff8be582","tid":2105942,"uid":11008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"咁迪士尼同海洋公園呢？d 病毒有基本法保護識轉彎唔會感染？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\